<li>"Using poetry to improve the quality of life and care for people with dementia," Helen Gregory University of Gloucestershire, Natural and Social Sciences, Cheltenham, UK (Received 9 December 2010; final version received 20 March 2011), Arts &amp; Health Vol. 3, No. 2, September 2011, 160.172</li>
