<p>My comments, or rather hopes with this project are really very simple. I deal with individuals who have been diagnosed with Alzheimer's Disease and other types of Dementia and have lived with it for years, by the time they come to our facility they may have lived in the community for 1 to 5 years before a loved knew that taking care of them at home was no longer a safe option.</p>
